fields.headline: Azed crossword 2,495
fields.bodyText: Click here to access the print version The Chambers Dictionary (2014) is recommended. Rules and requests £25 in book tokens for the first three correct solutions opened. Solutions postmarked no later than Saturday to: AZED No. 2,495, The Observer, 90 York Way, London N1 9GU. We regret that prizes for our puzzles are temporarily suspended.
